This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of panorama images from Google Street View, which falls under the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of a novel editing tool, which could fall under the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions the use of a "Turing-test"-like experiment to measure the quality of the system's creations, which suggests that the paper could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
